         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3168_0051"/><foreign xml:lang="en"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb41240">Aust<supplied>ria</supplied></rs></foreign></addrLine><addrLine>Herrn Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168934">IX. Frankga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 1</rs>.</addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3168_0050"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb118678">Chefoo China</rs>.</hi></p><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb141925">Beach Hotel</rs>.</hi></p><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb141923">Baby Tower Hill</rs>.</hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3168_0050"/><date when="1898-08-24">24. Augu<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t</date>.</dateline><salute rend="inline">Mein lieber Freund,</salute></opener><p>Ich hoffe, Du bi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t von Deiner <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L02856-1"/>Rei<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>e<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L02856-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L02845" subtype="See"/>.
               </note> ge<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>und zurückgekehrt. Ich wün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chte, daß ich auch<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chon wieder daheim wäre!
               Viele Grüße Dir, <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb10863">Richard</rs></hi> u. <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="person" ref="#pmb26392">Leo</rs></hi>!</p><closer>Dein <lb/><signed>Paul Goldmnn</signed></closer><postscript><p><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="org" ref="#pmb141921">Weinlaube</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb865">Klosterneuburg</rs>.</hi></p></postscript></div>
      </body>
